ZH: 你可以在图书馆的数据库中查阅相关资料。
EN: You can search for relevant information in the library's database.

ZH: 我建议你去医院查阅一下你的医疗记录。
EN: I suggest you go to the hospital to review your medical records.

ZH: 请到柜台查阅这本书的资料。
EN: Please go to the counter to look up the information about this book.

ZH: 教授要求我们查阅这个案例研究。
EN: The professor asked us to refer to this case study.

ZH: 我们需要查阅这份文件以做进一步研究。
EN: We need to consult this document for further research.

ZH: 查阅经验丰富的专家意见是明智之举。
EN: Consulting the opinions of experienced experts is a wise choice.

ZH: 你需要查阅这些资料才能完成这个项目。
EN: You need to refer to these materials to complete this project.

ZH: 这个资料库让用户方便地查阅所需信息。
EN: This database allows users to easily access the information they need.

ZH: 他们被允许在图书馆查阅这些特殊文献。
EN: They are allowed to view these special documents in the library.

ZH: 学生们可以在网上查阅课程资料。
EN: Students can access course materials online.

ZH: 请到网站上查阅最新动态。
EN: Please check the latest updates on the website.

ZH: 我们将查阅历史记录以了解过去的事件。
EN: We will review historical records to understand past events.

ZH: 请带上你的学生证以便查阅学校的资料。
EN: Please bring your student ID to access school information.

