EN: This database is available for researchers to consult.

ZH: 我们需要查阅公司档案以了解其历史。
EN: We need to refer to the company's records to understand its history.

ZH: 请查阅本手册以了解操作规程。
EN: Please consult this handbook to understand the operating procedures.

ZH: 教授建议学生查阅更多文献以支持他们的论点。
EN: The professor advises students to consult more literature to support their arguments.

ZH: 请到图书馆查阅这个重要的参考资料。
EN: Please go to the library to access this important reference material.

ZH: 我们需要查阅过去的数据以预测未来趋势。
EN: We need to refer to past data to predict future trends.
